snippet: Serena Williams overcame what she described as one of her worst sets and defeated the qualifier Eugenie Bouchard, 4-6, 6-2, 6-2.
abstract: Serena Williams defeats Eugenie Bouchard in her opening match at the Western & Southern Open tennis tournament; other opening matches noted.
